But Mr. Marſhall, (that famous and learned Divin
                  •
               ) deſired to know his Maieſties reaſon, why Hee would not hear the Engliſh Divines as well as the Scots, both Nations having entred into a Solemn League and Covenant, for the preſervation and defence of the Reformed Religion, now exercized in both Kingdomes.
